
It's simple code for displaying how to access C functions in nodejs using javascript.
First run c code and using it in nodejs.


run make start, the Makefile will automatically recompile any changes 

run in terminal:
make clean
make install
make start


run in terminal without make:

rm -f libmain.so & gcc -shared -o libmain.so -fPIC lib.c

rm -f build -r & npx node-gyp configure build

rm -f main & gcc main.c -o main

rm -f hello & gcc hello.c -o hello


run in Terminal:

npm install

npm start

